nmap <silent> <F5>  :20split<CR>:terminal perl %<CR>
nmap <silent> <F6>  :20split<CR>:terminal go run %<CR>
nmap <silent> <F7>  :20split<CR>:terminal javac % && java %:r<CR>
nmap   Q gq<CR>

